{"tid":826804,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼煮呀]—味噌牛油三文魚 Salmon with miso butter","createTime":"2018-09-18T13:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T00:57:18.000Z","uid":182683,"like":165,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"b923e5be69d0248034821b3691c0d472ba534a91","tid":826804,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"好耐冇出煮野食po！味噌牛油三文魚 ！我ig Story有片睇呀喂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n今日黎個簡單食譜，15分鐘煮到gordon ramsay級數嘅野食！FUCKING DELICIOUS！！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/210959_7357c64fad03c1af6a2f208f398ea8e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F210959_7357c64fad03c1af6a2f208f398ea8e1.png&h=30162ca3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n三文魚腩 一塊<br />\n白味噌 1湯匙<br />\n牛油(軟身) 4湯匙<br />\n鹽<br />\n黑胡椒<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n任何沙律<br />\n檸檬<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n做法：<br />\n1.醃魚<br />\n魚所有表面都撒層鹽同糖，大概鋪滿就可以，撒完放埋一邊等15分鐘。<br />\n依個步驟除左調味之外，可以迫左魚啲水出黎，令啲魚肉結實同埋魚味會濃啲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/211021_3c23111ded552987344567e60ff4aeb4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F211021_3c23111ded552987344567e60ff4aeb4.png&h=5ebf40ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.味噌牛油<br />\n牛油要軟身，將白味噌同牛油撈混。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/211048_00af87530e435888b9edca6dcdf6e4c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F211048_00af87530e435888b9edca6dcdf6e4c7.png&h=5ee36ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.處理魚<br />\n過左15分鐘，用水洗走啲調味料，用廚紙印乾魚身，用把好利嘅刀係魚皮𠝹幾下，不過唔好𠝹得太深，岩岩好𠝹到魚皮下面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/211204_959a472b8a4c269b1cb697bd9da868bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F211204_959a472b8a4c269b1cb697bd9da868bd.png&h=ec71c205&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/211206_2c62fafb9347bbadf5cb9de44ad2417a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F211206_2c62fafb9347bbadf5cb9de44ad2417a.png&h=b1f5ff80&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/211207_0504378515fc8954bc8ad6ac5c3d50a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F211207_0504378515fc8954bc8ad6ac5c3d50a2.png&h=933cdba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.煎脆魚皮<br />\n開大火落多少少油，煎到個皮脆，你會見到個邊金黃色就可以，大概30秒至1分鐘。<br />\n煎完夾起，啲油唔要，洗乾淨個pan。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/211229_999ab58236c7baa639fc1f325d2cb961.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F211229_999ab58236c7baa639fc1f325d2cb961.png&h=0b447e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/211231_5ce49f944abf97e5eea28f37fbe925ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F211231_5ce49f944abf97e5eea28f37fbe925ad.png&h=91798a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.煮第2次<br />\n轉中至細火，落1大湯匙味噌牛油，都係皮向下放番舊魚落去，一路用匙羹淋啲牛油上舊魚到，煮到你自己鍾意嘅熟成度。<br />\n要注意啲火唔好太大搞到啲味噌牛油煮燶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/211251_2b1928ba43fd15eca27cb7005fc0337a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F211251_2b1928ba43fd15eca27cb7005fc0337a.png&h=90a0aec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.上蹀<br />\n自己整個沙律放係底，放舊魚上去面落少少鹽同黑胡椒，鍾意香口啲可以淋少少頭先煮魚嘅牛油上去，切1/4個檸檬放係格離(我煎左個檸檬30秒,吱出黎啲汁食落會香啲)，搞掂！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/211314_fbc7db03d822e3a35646e331f1d85ddd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F211314_fbc7db03d822e3a35646e331f1d85ddd.png&h=e75006fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你煮完剩左嘅味噌牛油可以放幾星期，你鍾意拎黎煮肉/海鮮又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，食麵切細細舊溶係湯又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，啲扒煎完放舊係面又得！咩都得呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost&d=HBC7zYzG3YMcKN1Pc0EQt10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0f1a7acb\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost</a><br />\n<br />\nYoutube(整野食):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw%2Ffeatured&d=HBC7zYzG3YMcKN1Pc0EQt10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b9405f2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw/featured</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed2cfc9fd1aa7007be9d1afed61efa251222928","tid":826804,"uid":138040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:23:26.000Z","msg":"Ching sick ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a45c55b2c0c2268a4634e514886decd7c7deae","tid":826804,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:28:59.000Z","msg":"好似以好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bea8351410c758e973b22fe712861325b1f3694","tid":826804,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ed2cfc9fd1aa7007be9d1afed61efa251222928","tid":8268