706398c785abb78494bb710a865","tid":826804,"uid":22430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T17:51:53.000Z","msg":"之前你出過蕃茄cream意粉我跟住黎整好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出多啲post pleasssee"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"認真一問 其實我咁樣影相出po係未好過我成段片拍放youtube <br />\n我自己都覺得youtube啲片唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋用我太多時間 <br />\n如果唔整youtube我就可以出多啲依類po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:05:40.000Z","msg":"各有各好嘅 不過我偏向咁樣出post <br />\n因為睇片好快會過左一個step 我就要就住就住咁睇下停下又拉番轉頭咁 但如果你整甜品嘅可能片會比較好<br />\n其實你喱家圖文並茂已經好清楚lu 所以我覺得就咁出post就夠 你擺youtube link我禁都冇禁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"我都諗住唔拍咁大段片 我技術不足搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n主力影下相仲好 又可以出多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02393868acc0dd20375d6d4d95838a26f85df067","tid":826804,"uid":10830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:26:52.000Z","msg":"好似好好食！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ffff780287451afe0c61e10a4c157990410675","tid":826804,"uid":182683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c611997a890981fd9e2882c88db4b7a3acd6dd08","tid":826804,"uid":23360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T19:26:34.000Z","msg":"如果我用你呢個味噌牛油煎鯖魚得唔得？做法會唔會一樣？<br />\n<br />\n如果我用紅味噌又ok嗎？<br />\n<br />\n已訂閱youtube，以為你youtube係有呢個教學片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來無嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:29:57.000Z","msg":"其實依個煮嘅方法係岩用係啲厚身少少嘅肉到 <br />\n你鯖魚我諗通常都係薄身啲 你大火煎完都熟曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果再用牛油煮第2次會太熟<br />\n所以我解議你煎完搽啲牛油上去由佢溶開會最好<br />\n<br />\n紅味噌個味比較重 同魚夾埋會搶左啲味 但你叫如果真係要用就份量落少啲<br />\n<br />\n我ig有片呀 係igtv個到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  Youtube諗住唔搞住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452df868ccb93dbef62f708ea41cf451392033af","tid":826804,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"Fuck deli唔識串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31739888416aada318f33424983e8e4c6fc7c262","tid":826804,"uid":53784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"煮比本小姐食ok?"},{"pid":"4cf79f5cf867a3183c887bb28589b1d0244f1ec3","tid":826804,"uid":2811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"Follow左ig竟然有dm多謝支持<br />\n嚇死以為你識我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e06eee96b0e972315c2bf6068efb53dcc007d4","tid":826804,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"365d38fcb913299dab719174fe784a1e0b11dd3e","tid":826804,"uid":197998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f5bcb5fc5f4f9e645926d06d52cecc3ce8cc4ae","tid":826804,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aba52124a971f84b22d2c25966d6030afc6ce2d","tid":826804,"uid":197998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"其實出step by step相+caption係最方便睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"好！我唔整youtube住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  太辛苦整咁多野 <br />\n整完又唔靚 <br />\n我下次試下相加caption<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img 